name: Dobi
description:
A fight broke out in a nearby sari-sari store. Bystanders who were in the vicinity were trying to aid a cat who was swimming in his own pool of blood, with half of his face bashed in and barely able to utter a single word. Witnesses claim that the suspect of the assault was an orange male cat with a scar on the right side of his face and two earrings on his right ear. 

But the residents of Saint Valencia had never seen an orange cat for so long since the Meltdown. Everyone was baffled. Everyone was confused.

Could it be possible? Could it be possible that the orange cat they saw was the lost heir of House Silvis?

Could it be the sweet and curious cat they were fond of?

Could it be… Dobi the Firstborn?

But why hurt another individual? What are his motives? What is going on inside his mind?

What happened to him?
